name: Romantic Wedding Of Princess
description:
Romantic Wedding Of Princess is a fun-filled bride dress up game.
Hello, all my dear baby players, the barbie princess is going to married now and she is pregnant, the wedding will be a unique and sweet for them, join the game and help to makeup and dress up the princess barbie to be the beautiful bride now!

Game Features:
- Exquisite and fluent flash, adorable and cute prints
- Lively scenes design, nice background music
- Funny princess bride dress up game, more funs
- The beautiful princess barbie will be your dress up model
- Pretty wedding dress, hairstyles, jewels for you option and match
- Learn some dress up design and make up skills
